This project investigated the status and needs of manufacturing enterprises in the Internet Age.

### Responsibilities
- Conduct questionnaire surveys and interviews to collect raw data about manufacturing industries in Suzhou and Wuxi.
- Apply descriptive statistical methods to analyze the current status, problems, and needs regarding Internet Plus, open innovation, and transformation of manufacturing enterprises.
- Provide recommendations for promoting transformation based on the statistical analysis results.
